y":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:57:36.000Z","msg":"你確定樓下有人住?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac9414038e6605deccc4aab350943adb8555238","tid":389923,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:03:36.000Z","msg":"拎你枝棍落樓下捅佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d72bc011b6c9c3aec98b8ae7765e9b991145ef","tid":389923,"uid":48929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:07:33.000Z","msg":"你做過啲咩黎先"},{"pid":"645f766d48ef129790f3c939d3536bfabe908f8b","tid":389923,"uid":63734,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:09:43.000Z","msg":"篤得有拍子咪同佢dem返個beat先"},{"pid":"bf550f44f29603a865e9e5ce866081075a12998f","tid":389923,"uid":136639,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:15:53.000Z","msg":"聽過有人因為屋企有小朋友，成日噪到樓下做夜更嘅訓覺。樓下退休之後，成日半夜得閒就督天花板報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d270a6ec0a7e2c3fa635ce698712519e668974","tid":389923,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:17:54.000Z","msg":"拎把菜刀<br />\n係佢果層一邊磨一邊等佢 嚇下佢<br />\n搵人係地下睇下有冇保安果啲上黎<br />\n有就自己醒水返屋企<br />\n<br />\n上面既野千奇唔好學 如果唔係我報警拉你地"},{"pid":"230749dbcfe0a2b90dd32334c9e953b5e8e4c280","tid":389923,"uid":47278,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T19:28:10.000Z","msg":"震樓器防樓上噪音大功率免鑽孔震動馬達樓吵克星反擊利器震樓神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淘寶Link: <a href=\"http://e22a.com/h.rEyLCv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fe22a.com%2Fh.rEyLCv&d=HaY5XNuWdZBOgaSlRii9WaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6c8f15a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://e22a.com/h.rEyLCv</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打買個試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc097cfaca8427a78d8d8b2811783ab9c0b4cda8","tid":389923,"uid":47433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T21:00:01.000Z","msg":"係你嘈跌嘢佢先鑿你，定你明明好靜時佢都特登鑿你呀？<br />\n<br />\n香港有d樓d料真係好薄，我樓上不幸住咗兩個仆街仔，日日瘋狂蹦蹦跳跳傾灑玩具喺地，所以好明幾咁崩潰無助精神衰弱嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd3617f4929dcf11946fb90ee8b239c78840efd","tid":389923,"uid":6974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T21:47:18.000Z","msg":"以前樓上住過一對成日嗌交既家庭<br />\n總之一嘈就2-3個鐘 又大大力嘭門 又大聲嘈交 <br />\n投訴不果 鄰居勸喻不果 <br />\n<br />\n結果有鄰居（不是本人）印左一大疊<br />\nA4 寫住個家人欠債還錢 <br />\np曬圖 係咁寫啲衰野 仲扼人錢 <br />\n印完一疊放係既每一戶既信箱 <br />\n如是者個對家庭就搬左 <br />\n<br />\n至於樓主你可以同佢鬥癲 <br />\n<br />\n千其唔好做埋啲咩aa膠封鎖匙洞<br />\n唔好放埋蟲係佢門口呀"},{"pid":"00ba6cbfd66162c18c818b2c1c614e1e53022c82","tid":389923,"uid":98624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T22:22:37.000Z","msg":"屎蜢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6eb1f4e64499b3b9db3ec450b5260261d17176b","tid":389923,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:02:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鋪厚d 地毯得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要自己就癡線佬？"},{"pid":"fa436042b1b02cc4129497fcacffd1b81145d0ba","tid":389923,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你做過啲咩黎先</blockquote><br />\n無做過咩特別野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1768fa9591f5e27a8b456c83c521ce3b039c71","tid":389923,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係你嘈跌嘢佢先鑿你，定你明明好靜時佢都特登鑿你呀？<br />\n<br />\n香港有d樓d料真係好薄，我樓上不幸住咗兩個仆街仔，日日瘋狂蹦蹦跳跳傾灑玩具喺地，所以好明幾咁崩潰無助精神衰弱嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩樣都有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3823d08005bd1722a15f8d33b3ea35016cc0243c","tid":389923,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:17:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打住邊頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前就係呢個問題，搞極都搞唔掂所以搬走左</blockquote><br />\n係咪將軍澳</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6869c85b41966068ae1981acbc68c6fdcb8891bc","tid":389923,"uid":37225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:20:26.000Z","msg":"寄刀片"},{"pid":"48b025bc61c993ba6d1f0be30d52f7c063480f30","tid":389923,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打住邊頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前就係呢個問題，搞極都搞唔掂所以搬走左</blockquote><br />\n如果真係因爲咁而搬，我實翻黎玩勁佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242cc9f9b6c36f035ccae4b7056afbfbe9bc5e39","tid":389923,"uid":35160,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:39:32.000Z","msg":"你都識講你一跌野佢就有反應 <br />\n姐係你自己仆街在先 人地先玩9你<br />\n你仲好意思屌人痴線 <br />\n<br />\n同人傾下 認衰仔好過喇 仲想搞9人"},{"pid":"cc9881df961372ac1959174c759e7b15ef8f223f","tid":389923,"uid":131459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:47:19.000Z","msg":"呢個情況被騷擾方輸撚緊<br />\n只能夠搵管理公司警察調解<br />\n但其實冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4a809730174caee63b25a6987cdb37c2e300b7","tid":389923,"uid":13860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T23:58:07.000Z","msg":"我樓下都係咁，你果個維持左幾耐？"},{"pid":"c35fae094efb719f0e09429d190aab90ef343f2c","tid":389923,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我樓下都係咁，你果個維持左幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n八年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4045e05bda24c66a1da88c061a2a61377c0b83f3","tid":389923,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都識講你一跌野佢就有反應 <br />\n姐係你自己仆街在先 人地先玩9你<br />\n你仲好意思屌人痴線 <br />\n<br />\n同人傾下 認衰仔好過喇 仲想搞9人</blockquote><br />\n係屋企有聲發出其實好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5863681052d9169f1575b49f421c52449eaf4d4e","tid":389923,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個情況被騷擾方輸撚緊<br />\n只能夠搵管理公司警察調解<br />\n但其實冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以灰撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8700db834a57664435fb327ea61206af1441e3","tid":389923,"uid":8086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:45:54.000Z","msg":"樓主聽下樓上啲人講買共震喇叭啦，咁都唔敢用就抵比人嘈一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}